1: run the nsis-2.51-setup.exe
2: create APERTUSVR_SOURCE environment variable pointing to the root folder of your repository folder of ApertusVR
3: create APERTUSVR_BUILD environment variable pointing to the build folder of ApertusVR
4: drag&drop the make_installer.nsi to MakeNSISW (C:\Program Files (x86)\NSIS\makensisw.exe)
